  //- UTILITIES
  +content-section(contents[3], true)

    +p Text utility classes provides basic functionality such as alignment or text transform. There are also utility classes for text colors.

    +demo
      +demo-example
        p.text-left text left
        p.text-center text center
        p.text-right text right

        p
          span.text-vam text vertical align middle,
          span.text-vat.text-space-fix text vertical align top,
          span.text-vab.text-space-fix text vertical align bottom
          span.text-vabl.text-space-fix text vertical align baseline

        p
          span.text-transform-upper text transform upper
          br
          span.text-transform-none text transform none

        p
          span.text-bold text bold
          br
          span.text-semibold text semibold
          br
          span.text-regular text regular
          br
          span.text-italic text italic

        p.text-nospace text nospace
        p.text-space-half text space half

        p.text-nowrap <strong>Text nowrap</strong> ea dolor ea exercitation et esse incididunt ut Excepteur officia.

        p.text-ellipsis Text ellipsis ea dolor ea exercitation et esse incididunt ut Excepteur officia Ut sint cupidatat cupidatat nostrud veniam id nisi ut proident proident culpa consectetur occaecat velit ullamco in sunt sint deserunt adipisicing.

      +demo-code
        :code
          <p class="text-left">text left </p>
          <p class="text-center">text center</p>
          <p class="text-right">text right</p>

          <p>
            <span class="text-vam">text vertical align middle</span>
            <span class="text-vat text-space-fix">text vertical align top</span>
            <span class="text-vab text-space-fix">text vertical align bottom</span>
            <span class="text-vabl text-space-fix">text vertical align baseline</span>
          </p>

          <p>
            <span class="text-transform-upper">text transform upper</span><br>
            <span class="text-transform-normal">text transform normal</span><br>

            <span class="text-regular">text regular</span>
            <span class="text-bold">text bold</span><br>
            <span class="text-semibold">text semibold</span><br>
            <span class="text-italic">text italic</span>
          </p>

          <p class="text-space-half">text space half</p>
          <p class="text-nospace">text nospace</p>

          <p class="text-nowrap">...</p>
          <p class="text-ellipsis">...</p>
    //- end: demo

